summary: With an outgoing and open-minded characteristic, had much experience in event planning in university and a half year experience in the field of business development. Fluent in English, Chinese, and Korean; enthusiastic with different cultures, analytical thinking, and result-driven.  Graduated from TIAS business school with a master degree in business administration and specialization in business analytics.
